# Launch Strategy

Don't wait for perfection.

Release to:

* Yourself
* Family
* Friends
* A few trusted users

Observe how they actually use the app.

---

# Listen to Real Users

Example:

You think users want:

```text
Beautiful graphs.
```

Users actually ask for:

```text
Support for more laboratories.
```

Always prioritize real feedback over assumptions.

---

# Success Metrics

Track simple numbers:

```text
Users Registered

↓

Reports Uploaded

↓

OCR Success Rate

↓

AI Summaries Generated

↓

Returning Users
```

These metrics tell you whether the app is improving.

