# 💡 Founder Recommendation

Based on everything we've planned over the last 51 days, I'd suggest a slight adjustment to your roadmap.

Instead of thinking:

```text
Finish building the app

↓

Release it
```

Think:

```text
Build the smallest useful version

↓

Release to 10 users

↓

Improve based on feedback

↓

Release to 100 users

↓

Improve again

↓

Scale gradually
```

This reduces risk and helps you build features that people actually use.

